-- Novatek Hires Former Rosneft Investor Relations Head Palivoda
-- B y   A n n a   S h i r y a e v s k a y a
-- 2012-08-14T14:37:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-14/novatek-hires-former-rosneft-investor-relations-head-palivoda.html
OAO Novatek,  Russia ’s second-largest
natural-gas producer, hired Alexander Palivoda, the former head
of  investor relations  at state-run oil producer  OAO Rosneft. (ROSN)   “We have hired a new IR person,” Mark Gyetvay, Novatek
chief financial officer, said on a conference call. “His
starting day was today.”  Rosneft’s press service wasn’t available for comment when
contacted by Bloomberg News.  To contact the reporter on this story:
